{"tid":1515533,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣組請入] 開學文宣全面進攻校園","createTime":"2019-08-29T07:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:36:40.000Z","uid":173334,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"af41434a515593a6056c2bac767d8cc703130aa1","tid":1515533,"uid":173334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:54:49.000Z","msg":"小弟不才, 唔識設計文宣圖<br />\n但係有個建議就係設計D關於黑警父母既文宣貼係校園/校外當眼位置<br />\n務求D狗仔狗女睇清楚佢地D狗父狗母所作所為<br />\n<br />\n建議整D關於黑警係非禮犯, 變態虐待狂,黑社會<br />\nD圖可以簡單D, 令小學生都可以睇得明<br />\n希望D狗仔狗女睇到之後番屋企質問班黑警<br />\n<br />\n林鄭搞到咁多家庭因為黃藍分化, 我地都唔可以放過班黑警<br />\n以文宣製造黑警家庭不和, 以小孩良知喚醒班狗"},{"pid":"d2788db05eb6f63d23178fa90e589885225664f3","tid":1515533,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea69a396f08d04d4217bd1c06425cab055622077","tid":1515533,"uid":173334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a7cdc7a120ae2e03604f2cc01493ce9f2d8ad9ef","tid":1515533,"uid":173334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:01:19.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"1fa11de8389c4f64902e072d5a368ff20bff34d1","tid":1515533,"uid":776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bacebd1557c94e6780a31d03559ec4c939882c4","tid":1515533,"uid":173334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:37:33.000Z","msg":"831 901 902"},{"pid":"b41e6869a948f71e2b561d08e24f891613ca7505","tid":1515533,"uid":173334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea72f6b213b4bad9166d28f5e70e4744e7be8eb","tid":1515533,"uid":17